cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL

This paper deals with ontology integration and meta-modelling, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of Description Logic and tableau algorithm also suggests a connection to database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the concept of meta-modelling is also relevant to programming languages (cs.PL).
